Class UMLElement

@ClassVersion(sourceVersion="$Id: UMLElement.java 976 2022-01-06 11:39:58Z tquadrat $") @API(status=INTERNAL, since="0.0.5") public abstract class UMLElement extends Object implements Element
The wrapper for an Element instance, enhanced by information needed for the creation of the UML graph.

      public static final boolean isAPI(Element element)
      Tests whether the given element is part of an API or not. The consideration is, that only element that are either public or protected are part of the API of a class.
      Parameters:
